UsageCost: Average $0.60/kWh (Tesla), $0.90/kWh (non-Tesla). Rates are frequently adjusted based on demand. For up-to-date information see Tesla mobile app.
GeneralComments: Supercharger open to non-Tesla EVs covered by NACS agreement ( https://www.tesla.com/NACS ). EVs with CCS1 charging port need an adapter provided by vehicle manufacturer. Tesla account and mobile app (Tesla) required for payment (pay-per-use). Plug & Charge payment option available for some EVs (Ford, Rivian). No credit card reader at the charger.
